dct_description_sm: Inside of brochure features pictoral map of the Washington Crossing State Park indicating approved campsites, picnic areas and latrines. Rest of page features descriptions of the park, the wildlife santuary and the McKonkey Ferry House. Two photographs depict the ferry house and the picnic area at Sullivan Grove.
